WEBVTT

00:00:00.480 --> 00:00:03.429
This is what I have for you. I

00:00:03.439 --> 00:00:05.990
want to show you, starting off, one of the

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:07.749
prophetic words that I've given you all

00:00:07.759 --> 00:00:10.709
in prayer was about the fish. Do you

00:00:10.719 --> 00:00:12.629
remember I said I saw the fish

00:00:12.639 --> 00:00:15.829
rolling in on the waves?

00:00:15.839 --> 00:00:18.630
Whenever I was seeing, I saw thousands of

00:00:18.640 --> 00:00:21.109
fish rolling in, and I said they're

00:00:21.119 --> 00:00:22.790
coming up from the water. I don't

00:00:22.800 --> 00:00:24.950
know what caused this, but I could just

00:00:24.960 --> 00:00:26.870
see them, and as they were coming in, they

00:00:26.880 --> 00:00:29.029
were on the shore. There were so

00:00:29.039 --> 00:00:30.710
many of them, and the

00:00:30.720 --> 00:00:32.229
Lord told me it's going to stink because

00:00:32.239 --> 00:00:34.389
there were so many dead fish. Well, one

00:00:34.399 --> 00:00:35.750
of my viewers—I don't know if it was

00:00:35.750 --> 00:00:35.760
Facebook—somebody

00:00:35.760 --> 00:00:37.830
sent this and said, "Hey,

00:00:37.840 --> 00:00:40.950
did you see all the dead fish

00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:43.190
from the lake? It wasn't from the ocean,

00:00:43.200 --> 00:00:46.310
but this is what's

00:00:46.310 --> 00:00:46.320
happening."I

00:00:46.320 --> 00:00:47.590
don't know what would cause this.

00:00:47.600 --> 00:00:49.590
They're saying there are pockets

00:00:49.590 --> 00:00:49.600
where

00:00:49.600 --> 00:00:51.990
the oxygen in the water is causing

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:53.750
them to die, and all this

00:00:53.760 --> 00:00:56.150
stuff, right?

00:00:56.160 --> 00:00:58.229
But I was seeing all the fish rolling in

00:00:58.239 --> 00:01:00.069
on the waves.

00:01:00.079 --> 00:01:03.110
So, this is what I saw.

00:01:03.120 --> 00:01:05.830
I wanted Braden to play this

00:01:05.840 --> 00:01:10.630
little clip for y'all.

00:01:10.640 --> 00:01:12.469
Do you see all these dead fish? Can they

00:01:12.479 --> 00:01:14.789
see all these dead fish? This is

00:01:14.799 --> 00:01:16.789
serious. I don't know what would cause

00:01:16.799 --> 00:01:17.990
all that, but they're saying maybe

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:19.190
oxygen. They don't know what's in the

00:01:19.200 --> 00:01:20.390
water, but something's causing all these

00:01:20.400 --> 00:01:21.749
fish. But this is what the Lord was

00:01:21.759 --> 00:01:24.390
showing me—another glimpse into the

00:01:24.400 --> 00:01:26.310
future. And the Lord's warning us of

00:01:26.320 --> 00:01:28.550
things. I even saw this in

00:01:28.560 --> 00:01:31.910
California, all up the coast, all over

00:01:31.920 --> 00:01:35.030
Oregon, all over the area—major fish

00:01:35.040 --> 00:01:37.109
coming in by the thousands, tens of

00:01:37.119 --> 00:01:40.069
thousands dead on the top of the water.

00:01:40.079 --> 00:01:43.190
And that right there is exactly what I

00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:46.870
was shown. Just like that. And it is

00:01:46.880 --> 00:01:48.950
nasty. But I was like, isn't that

00:01:48.960 --> 00:01:50.550
amazing? And they don't know what's

00:01:50.560 --> 00:01:52.710
coming. Maybe they do now. This video is

00:01:52.720 --> 00:01:57.270
a couple days old as I receive this, but

00:01:57.280 --> 00:01:59.749
I just thought of the prophetic side of it,

00:01:59.759 --> 00:02:02.069
that as watchmen, the Lord shows us

00:02:02.079 --> 00:02:04.550
what's coming and we pray over things.

00:02:04.560 --> 00:02:06.950
It's pretty amazing how fast things are

00:02:06.960 --> 00:02:09.669
happening. It's not like

00:02:09.679 --> 00:02:11.270
before, where we always talked about how things would

00:02:11.280 --> 00:02:13.030
happen and we would see them,

00:02:13.030 --> 00:02:13.040
but

00:02:13.040 --> 00:02:15.190
it would take weeks, months, or years for

00:02:15.200 --> 00:02:16.869
stuff to manifest. Now it's

00:02:16.879 --> 00:02:18.070
happening in days.

00:02:18.080 --> 00:02:19.270
Yes!

00:02:19.280 --> 00:02:21.110
And I'm like, "Wow, Lord, look at

00:02:21.110 --> 00:02:21.120
the

00:02:21.120 --> 00:02:23.030
signs

00:02:23.030 --> 00:02:23.040
of

00:02:23.040 --> 00:02:26.150
the

00:02:26.150 --> 00:02:26.160
times."You

00:02:26.160 --> 00:02:28.390
can stop it if you want to. So then

00:02:28.400 --> 00:02:30.390
the other part was praying over the

00:02:30.400 --> 00:02:34.550
escalation of war. I heard it again.

00:02:34.560 --> 00:02:37.910
So I'll go over my visitation

00:02:37.920 --> 00:02:42.390
experience, what happened in my sleep

00:02:42.400 --> 00:02:45.350
out of nowhere. I mean, this is like

00:02:45.350 --> 00:02:45.360
5:00

00:02:45.360 --> 00:02:47.750
in the morning. I wake up, and I feel the

00:02:47.760 --> 00:02:49.990
Holy Ghost and fire all over my body.

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:53.670
As I

00:02:53.680 --> 00:02:56.229
breathe in, I feel the anointing and the

00:02:56.239 --> 00:02:58.070
power of the Holy Spirit just flowing

00:02:58.080 --> 00:03:00.550
through me. And all of a

00:03:00.550 --> 00:03:00.560
sudden—this

00:03:00.560 --> 00:03:02.390
is what's interesting—it wasn't a

00:03:02.400 --> 00:03:05.110
dream, but it was a night vision.

00:03:05.120 --> 00:03:06.470
That's the only way... I've never had

00:03:06.480 --> 00:03:09.830
this before, but I was

00:03:09.840 --> 00:03:11.670
asleep, you know, in between sleep

00:03:11.680 --> 00:03:14.149
and awake. And I'm seeing,

00:03:14.159 --> 00:03:16.630
and He says to me, "Brandon, I'm

00:03:16.640 --> 00:03:19.910
asking you to help me with

00:03:19.910 --> 00:03:19.920
something."And

00:03:19.920 --> 00:03:22.869
I paused. I said,

00:03:22.869 --> 00:03:22.879
because

00:03:22.879 --> 00:03:24.630
I'm asleep,

00:03:24.630 --> 00:03:24.640
"Lord,

00:03:24.640 --> 00:03:26.869
what can I

00:03:26.879 --> 00:03:29.030
help you

00:03:29.030 --> 00:03:29.040
with?"And

00:03:29.040 --> 00:03:31.990
He said, "There's a

00:03:32.000 --> 00:03:33.910
youth

00:03:33.920 --> 00:03:36.710
group across the street."And I

00:03:36.720 --> 00:03:38.149
saw the youth group, and He said,

00:03:38.159 --> 00:03:40.710
"There's a young man that's going to be

00:03:40.720 --> 00:03:42.630
coming to this youth group

00:03:42.630 --> 00:03:42.640
whom

00:03:42.640 --> 00:03:45.030
I'm calling into

00:03:45.040 --> 00:03:47.110
ministry. I want him to be in

00:03:47.120 --> 00:03:48.789
ministry. There's a call

00:03:48.799 --> 00:03:50.149
on his life, but he doesn't

00:03:50.159 --> 00:03:52.390
know me yet.

00:03:52.400 --> 00:03:54.630
Pray for this young man."And I could

00:03:54.640 --> 00:03:56.550
see this young man. He

00:03:56.560 --> 00:03:58.630
looked like a football player,

00:03:58.640 --> 00:04:01.670
and it's an actual

00:04:01.670 --> 00:04:01.680
person—I

00:04:01.680 --> 00:04:03.270
know that for a fact now after

00:04:03.280 --> 00:04:05.509
the Lord showed me. So the

00:04:05.519 --> 00:04:07.429
Lord had me praying for this young man,

00:04:07.439 --> 00:04:09.910
and He said, "I want him to come over to

00:04:09.920 --> 00:04:12.149
the youth group across the street during

00:04:12.159 --> 00:04:15.110
the fall,

00:04:15.120 --> 00:04:16.949
and I've asked other people to do what

00:04:16.959 --> 00:04:18.310
I'm asking you to do, but they've all

00:04:18.320 --> 00:04:22.069
told me

00:04:22.069 --> 00:04:22.079
no."I

00:04:22.079 --> 00:04:25.110
had saved some money. I told

00:04:25.120 --> 00:04:26.710
Diana we've been saving because we

00:04:26.720 --> 00:04:28.550
want to remodel our house, but we don't

00:04:28.560 --> 00:04:29.749
tell everybody because we don't believe

00:04:29.759 --> 00:04:31.990
in debt. We do Financial Peace

00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:34.390
University. We believe in

00:04:34.400 --> 00:04:36.390
not borrowing money as much as possible.

00:04:36.400 --> 00:04:38.629
If you have to in an emergency, you

00:04:38.639 --> 00:04:40.950
know, but we believe in paying cash for things.

00:04:40.960 --> 00:04:42.629
That's just the way we've

00:04:42.639 --> 00:04:44.469
always lived. We don't believe in credit

00:04:44.479 --> 00:04:46.230
cards. We don't believe in things like

00:04:46.240 --> 00:04:49.670
that. We don't borrow;

00:04:49.680 --> 00:04:51.670
we're not slave to the

00:04:51.670 --> 00:04:51.680
lender.

00:04:51.680 --> 00:04:53.909
The only thing is like our

00:04:53.919 --> 00:04:55.670
student loans or whatever, but I'm just

00:04:55.680 --> 00:04:59.189
saying paying things down deliberately,

00:04:59.199 --> 00:05:02.870
living by faith. So

00:05:02.880 --> 00:05:04.629
we wanted to fix up our bathrooms

00:05:04.639 --> 00:05:06.150
and do things around our house, so we

00:05:06.160 --> 00:05:07.590
have our own little account. We've

00:05:07.600 --> 00:05:09.670
been putting money in there, and we got

00:05:09.680 --> 00:05:11.189
it up because we had a guy come

00:05:11.199 --> 00:05:12.629
out and say, "Hey, this is what it's

00:05:12.639 --> 00:05:14.710
going to cost to remodel it all, fix

00:05:14.720 --> 00:05:16.469
up your bathrooms, and update

00:05:16.469 --> 00:05:16.479
everything."We

00:05:16.479 --> 00:05:17.590
were really excited about it.

00:05:17.600 --> 00:05:19.590
It's something private we had between us

00:05:19.590 --> 00:05:19.600
that

00:05:19.600 --> 00:05:21.590
we don't talk about. So we put some

00:05:21.600 --> 00:05:23.110
money back—kept putting money back—and the

00:05:23.110 --> 00:05:23.120
account was

00:05:23.120 --> 00:05:24.710
getting really big. We were

00:05:24.720 --> 00:05:25.749
excited about it because we had the

00:05:25.759 --> 00:05:27.590
money to redo what we wanted

00:05:27.590 --> 00:05:27.600
to

00:05:27.600 --> 00:05:30.629
have redone. Then we had the

00:05:30.639 --> 00:05:32.390
leak happen in our house, and

00:05:32.400 --> 00:05:35.110
we were believing God

00:05:35.120 --> 00:05:37.749
for stuff, you know. Well, we put the

00:05:37.759 --> 00:05:39.670
money back and

00:05:39.680 --> 00:05:41.110
we didn't say anything, but

00:05:41.120 --> 00:05:43.590
we were right at that point. And the

00:05:43.600 --> 00:05:45.749
Lord said to me,

00:05:45.759 --> 00:05:47.350
"Brandon, I've asked these people to

00:05:47.360 --> 00:05:50.469
help me. I know it's above what you

00:05:50.479 --> 00:05:51.909
tithe, and I know it's above what I've

00:05:51.919 --> 00:05:54.390
already asked you to do, but could you

00:05:54.400 --> 00:05:55.749
help with the youth building

00:05:55.759 --> 00:06:00.950
that they're trying to

00:06:00.950 --> 00:06:00.960
build?"I

00:06:00.960 --> 00:06:04.390
said, "Woo, that's hard."I said,

00:06:04.400 --> 00:06:07.510
"Lord, I told you

00:06:07.520 --> 00:06:10.469
I'll do anything you ask me to

00:06:10.469 --> 00:06:10.479
do,"but

00:06:10.479 --> 00:06:13.510
my flesh was irritated, just

00:06:13.520 --> 00:06:16.150
being real, because I worked so hard to

00:06:16.160 --> 00:06:17.670
save that money. I told Him,

00:06:17.680 --> 00:06:20.790
"My flesh is annoyed, but I told

00:06:20.800 --> 00:06:23.110
you I would do anything you

00:06:23.120 --> 00:06:26.390
ever asked me to do, so I'll do

00:06:26.390 --> 00:06:26.400
it."And

00:06:26.400 --> 00:06:29.189
instantaneously,

00:06:29.199 --> 00:06:30.870
you deal with...

00:06:30.880 --> 00:06:32.309
I'm just like

00:06:32.319 --> 00:06:34.469
anybody, y'all, I deal with

00:06:34.469 --> 00:06:34.479
the

00:06:34.479 --> 00:06:36.790
flesh too. My flesh was like,

00:06:36.800 --> 00:06:39.590
"That's my money I've saved.

00:06:39.600 --> 00:06:42.710
And you're asking me to give

00:06:42.710 --> 00:06:42.720
that?"He

00:06:42.720 --> 00:06:45.029
said, "I desire it to be done before

00:06:45.039 --> 00:06:47.110
the fall. I need help. Would you

00:06:47.120 --> 00:06:49.510
help me?"So I told Diana. And Diana,

00:06:49.520 --> 00:06:53.350
always sweet Diana, goes, "If

00:06:53.360 --> 00:06:54.870
that's what the Lord is saying, let's

00:06:54.880 --> 00:06:56.230
just do it."I wanted her

00:06:56.240 --> 00:06:58.390
to be like, "No, we're not doing

00:06:58.390 --> 00:06:58.400
that."I

00:06:58.400 --> 00:06:59.909
thought, "I can blame it on her,

00:06:59.919 --> 00:07:03.270
Lord. See, she said no,

00:07:03.280 --> 00:07:06.629
it's her

00:07:06.629 --> 00:07:06.639
fault."But

00:07:06.639 --> 00:07:08.070
she was

00:07:08.080 --> 00:07:09.830
so nice about it and said, "Well, if that's

00:07:09.840 --> 00:07:11.430
what the Lord is saying, honey,

00:07:11.440 --> 00:07:13.189
let's just do it."I thought, "Please

00:07:13.199 --> 00:07:15.909
don't say

00:07:15.909 --> 00:07:15.919
that."I

00:07:15.919 --> 00:07:17.589
was really mad at her

00:07:17.599 --> 00:07:19.670
then, I really was, because I wanted

00:07:19.680 --> 00:07:21.189
to have a scapegoat and say,

00:07:21.199 --> 00:07:23.749
"You know what, Diana? I don't

00:07:23.759 --> 00:07:25.430
blame you. It's all right,"and then go,

00:07:25.440 --> 00:07:26.710
"God, it's her problem,

00:07:26.720 --> 00:07:29.830
she's the one that did

00:07:29.830 --> 00:07:29.840
it."That's

00:07:29.840 --> 00:07:33.110
just where I was, just being real,

00:07:33.120 --> 00:07:36.550
okay? I'm just being real. And so,

00:07:36.560 --> 00:07:39.589
when she said it so nicely, I was just like,

00:07:39.599 --> 00:07:44.560
"Okay, flesh. Okay,

00:07:44.570 --> 00:07:46.950
flesh."Thank

00:07:46.960 --> 00:07:49.749
you, God, for an obedient wife

00:07:49.749 --> 00:07:49.759
who

00:07:49.759 --> 00:07:54.070
loves the Lord. She had

00:07:54.080 --> 00:07:55.670
a good attitude about it; my attitude

00:07:55.670 --> 00:07:55.680
was

00:07:55.680 --> 00:07:58.150
still stinky. I prayed

00:07:58.160 --> 00:08:00.230
over it for the whole day.

00:08:00.230 --> 00:08:00.240
Then

00:08:00.240 --> 00:08:02.550
I reached out to the pastor, and I

00:08:02.560 --> 00:08:05.189
was trying to give hints: "Hey, do you

00:08:05.199 --> 00:08:06.790
like going out to eat? Do you like going

00:08:06.800 --> 00:08:07.990
to this certain place?"and he acted

00:08:08.000 --> 00:08:09.189
like he was too busy and didn't want

00:08:09.199 --> 00:08:10.710
anything to do with it. So I thought,

00:08:10.720 --> 00:08:14.230
"Well, there's a closed door.

00:08:14.240 --> 00:08:16.230
There's a closed door."Because I felt

00:08:16.240 --> 00:08:17.909
inside that I was going to be obedient, but if

00:08:17.919 --> 00:08:20.710
he says no, then it's not God. I'm

00:08:20.720 --> 00:08:24.309
not going to give that money then.

00:08:24.319 --> 00:08:26.629
And so it's not funny. It's really real.

00:08:26.639 --> 00:08:29.189
And so I say, "Hey, do you like

00:08:29.199 --> 00:08:30.950
going to Wild Fork? Do you want to go

00:08:30.960 --> 00:08:32.550
out to eat?"He didn't respond, "Oh

00:08:32.560 --> 00:08:33.829
yeah, it's a good place to

00:08:33.829 --> 00:08:33.839
eat."But

00:08:33.839 --> 00:08:36.230
never anything else. I thought, "Okay,

00:08:36.240 --> 00:08:42.230
close call. It's not like I had to give

00:08:42.230 --> 00:08:42.240
it."It

00:08:42.240 --> 00:08:46.070
just, you know, we

00:08:46.080 --> 00:08:47.509
tell you these things. I'm

00:08:47.519 --> 00:08:50.150
trying to help y'all; it's helping me

00:08:50.160 --> 00:08:53.030
help. So,

00:08:53.040 --> 00:08:55.990
to make a long story short, I get up and

00:08:56.000 --> 00:08:58.310
it's Sunday morning and the Lord

00:08:58.320 --> 00:09:01.990
said, "Not only do I want you to give

00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:05.110
the money, but this time I don't want

00:09:05.120 --> 00:09:07.750
you to hand it to them to hand to

00:09:07.760 --> 00:09:09.670
the pastor personally and give them

00:09:09.680 --> 00:09:13.670
this check. You are to try to

00:09:13.680 --> 00:09:15.590
deflect the glory."And he

00:09:15.600 --> 00:09:16.550
corrected me on some things. This is

00:09:16.560 --> 00:09:18.710
where I'm going to go with it. He said,

00:09:18.720 --> 00:09:20.949
"This is not to give you glory about how

00:09:20.959 --> 00:09:22.550
much money you're going to give to the

00:09:22.560 --> 00:09:24.870
youth program for this

00:09:24.880 --> 00:09:27.110
building. I want you to do this

00:09:27.120 --> 00:09:29.269
privately, and I want you to put it in

00:09:29.279 --> 00:09:32.710
the bucket and just let that check sit

00:09:32.720 --> 00:09:35.030
in that bucket,

00:09:35.040 --> 00:09:36.790
and you're not going to get any man's

00:09:36.800 --> 00:09:39.110
praise at all. Not a thank you

00:09:39.120 --> 00:09:42.389
from them personally, like, 'Please

00:09:42.399 --> 00:09:44.389
pray over this

00:09:44.399 --> 00:09:45.750
seed.'Do

00:09:45.760 --> 00:09:47.590
you understand? This is a huge deal for

00:09:47.590 --> 00:09:47.600
us."And

00:09:47.600 --> 00:09:50.230
so my flesh was like—when he

00:09:50.240 --> 00:09:52.150
said that, I was even more disturbed. I

00:09:52.160 --> 00:09:55.509
went, "Are you kidding

00:09:55.509 --> 00:09:55.519
me?"So,

00:09:55.519 --> 00:09:59.750
I sat on the back row like I always do,

00:09:59.760 --> 00:10:01.910
and that bucket came by. And I was like,

00:10:01.920 --> 00:10:03.670
"I'm looking for a Holy Ghost choir, like

00:10:03.680 --> 00:10:05.430
an Abraham experience saying, 'Don't

00:10:05.440 --> 00:10:09.269
kill the son. It's

00:10:09.279 --> 00:10:11.670
okay. I've heard the angel

00:10:11.670 --> 00:10:11.680
come.'You're

00:10:11.680 --> 00:10:13.269
looking for

00:10:13.279 --> 00:10:15.350
the angel to say—the parting of

00:10:15.360 --> 00:10:17.110
the sky and looking for the angel to

00:10:17.120 --> 00:10:18.710
go, 'It's okay. You don't have to give

00:10:18.720 --> 00:10:21.509
it. I see your

00:10:21.509 --> 00:10:21.519
heart.'"But

00:10:21.519 --> 00:10:23.910
that didn't happen.

00:10:23.920 --> 00:10:25.910
It didn't happen. And as I put that

